\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{5}=\frac{-i}{4!}\epsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\sigma}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\gamma^{5},S_{\mu\nu}\right]=0
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

与洛伦兹群（旋量表示）的所有生成元对易。所以狄拉克场构造的表示一定是可约表示。
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

在Wyel表象下，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{5}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-1 & 0\\
0 & 1
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L=\frac{1}{2}(1-\gamma^{5}),R=\frac{1}{2}(1+\gamma^{5}),\{\gamma^{5},\gamma^{\mu}\}=0,L^{2}=1,R^{2}=1,\gamma^{0}L^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=R
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & 0\\
0 & 0
\end{array}\right),R=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & 0\\
0 & 1
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L\gamma^{\mu}=\gamma^{\mu}R,R\gamma^{\mu}=\gamma^{\mu}L
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}R\gamma^{\mu}L\psi$
\end_inset

是合理的组合，
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

也就是说
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi_{L}}=(L\psi)^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=\psi^{\dagger}L^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=\psi^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}\gamma^{0}L\gamma^{0}=\bar{\psi}R$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold

\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

场的左手分量是
\begin_inset Formula $L.\psi$
\end_inset

,右手分量是
\begin_inset Formula $R.\psi$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}$
\end_inset

场的左手分量是
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}.R$
\end_inset

，右手分量是
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}.L$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{\psi}_{L}=\bar{\psi}.R,\quad\bar{\psi}_{R}=\bar{\psi}.L
\]

\end_inset


